name: The Architect's Pact
description: Extremely rare and unique. This OBJKT is a pact between Creator and Collector. Whomever collects this gains the ability to request a special, custom 1/1 objkt to be made exclusively for them by TradScape at no charge to the collector. The collector may suggest the theme and subject of the objkt within the world of TradScape. This privilege may be used once for every new owner of The Architect's Pact.
